    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a parts car or a significant restoration project. The engine currently runs but has a noticeable knock and several leaks, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. The body shows significant signs of wear, including rust on the quarter panels and several deep scratches, and the interior requires a complete overhaul due to heavy staining and torn upholstery. It is recommended that the buyer hauls the vehicle rather than driving it away.",
