    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is strong and reliable, with a smooth engine and transmission that make it a pleasure to drive. The exterior remains attractive with its original paint, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches typical of a used car. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. It is a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for a well-maintained vehicle that still has plenty of life left.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
