      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous care and uncompromising maintenance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen that remains indistinguishable from its original showroom state, offering a refined driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
