    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a pristine example of BMW M-division engineering, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring dual-VANOS and individual throttle bodies. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with a documented rod bearing service and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Power is transmitted through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional traction and corner-exit stability. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping and bushing elasticity, offering the communicative feedback synonymous with the chassis. Finished in concours-quality paint with a flawless interior, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the purist collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
